                                                   Morkel puts SA on top
                      
	Dhaka: Morne Morkel claimed his maiden Test five-wicket haul to help South Africa dismiss Bangladesh for 192 on Day I of the first Test Friday.         
	Steve Bucknor also returned to Test umpiring after the Sydney Test.           (REUTERS)                                                                                                                   
